dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Vilas County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase "Vilas_PLSS_2017.gdb". [The current control point on the surface of the earth and its associated current coordinate value, generally determined by a surveying process and used to define an extremity of a boundary.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
